00:31:25,090 --> 00:31:34,190
Scott: And the best way to describe the cloud to people who don't know, or even to yourself, if you think you know, is say a sentence with the word "the cloud" in it and use the word "the cloud" properly.

617
00:31:34,270 --> 00:31:38,306
Scott: Then rewrite the sentence and replace "the cloud" with the words "someone else's

618
00:31:38,346 --> 00:31:38,708
