619
00:31:40,572 --> 00:31:44,030
Scott: It's like, yeah, all my photos are stored in the cloud by Flickr.

620
00:31:44,610 --> 00:31:48,010
Scott: All my photos are stored on someone else's computer, run by Flickr.

621
00:31:48,512 --> 00:31:56,210
