625
00:32:08,830 --> 00:32:13,039
Rym: No, no, no, you've got to have backups on your attached storage.

626
00:32:13,360 --> 00:32:19,260
Rym: that itself is backed up somehow, right?

627
00:32:19,662 --> 00:32:20,810
Scott: That's where you have to have things.

628
00:32:21,030 --> 00:32:26,910
Scott: And sometimes it's okay to back things up on someone else's computer from someone else's computer.

629
00:32:27,090 --> 00:32:29,649
